Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.85,0:00:07.81,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, next...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.59,0:00:11.30,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Those in favour of a café, raise your hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.74,0:00:12.27,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,I am!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.27,0:00:13.24,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Me too!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.85,0:00:15.61,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Those who want to have a dance?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.98,0:00:19.96,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,No takers, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.74,0:00:22.99,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,This class sure hates breaking a sweat...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.74,0:00:26.41,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Well then, those who are in favour of a harmonica?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.83,0:00:28.25,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Me! Me! I am!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.48,0:00:31.22,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it's decided then.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.89,0:00:34.26,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Dear mother,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.54,0:00:37.52,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm sorry for the late reply.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.20,0:00:41.14,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm still the same.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.72,0:00:44.84,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Walking from school to the dormitory and back.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.11,0:00:47.67,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}There's nothing to worry about.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.46,0:01:00.76,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}However, I've been...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.11,0:01:03.16,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,There you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.16,0:01:04.05,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Naito!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.64,0:01:06.61,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.72,0:01:08.39,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you free later?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.59,0:01:11.56,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have any plans?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.56,0:01:13.27,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,No... Not really...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.55,0:01:16.79,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Good! Could you do me a little favour?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.49,0:01:19.78,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,I need you to deliver this to Sparrow's Forest.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.60,0:01:23.75,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Why me?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.75,0:01:25.39,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,It's on your way back, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.39,0:01:26.83,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,You can do it, can't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.83,0:01:28.55,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,It's still two stations away.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.06,0:01:32.63,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Since I need to go to the staff meeting and the school year meeting...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.63,0:01:34.31,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm really sorry, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.61,0:01:36.53,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Can I do it tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.93,0:01:40.79,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,All the students of Sparrow's Forest are taking the day off.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.79,0:01:44.13,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I've been asked to check on them.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.43,0:01:46.26,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess there's no other way.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.26,0:01:47.14,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.94,0:01:49.43,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks a lot!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.43,0:01:50.81,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,My darling, Miss Naito!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.20,0:02:04.42,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,The first train will be arriving shortly.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.12,0:02:08.25,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Please remain behind the yellow line until then.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.31,0:02:12.86,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}However, I've been pushing myself lately.{\i0}
