Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.09,0:02:59.70,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Who is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.11,0:03:03.29,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Naito?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.71,0:03:05.00,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Enjouji.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.36,0:03:07.22,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, Miss Rabbit!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.22,0:03:09.42,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you going to let me in?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.49,0:03:10.66,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.99,0:03:13.64,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, but I can't allow you in here!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.64,0:03:14.92,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a mumps outbreak!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.13,0:03:17.93,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Although, I could make an exception if you have other business here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.66,0:03:19.56,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,What should we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.56,0:03:22.20,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Some girl from school is here, probably to check on us.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.57,0:03:24.08,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Just a little more...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.32,0:03:25.99,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm afraid that's not possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.99,0:03:27.68,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,What will we do if they found out about the fake illness?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.98,0:03:29.65,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.71,0:03:32.50,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Since you said you had mumps...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.50,0:03:34.25,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,...everybody took the day off from school.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.71,0:03:36.49,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Then just for tonight!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.49,0:03:39.98,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be alright! I just want to be with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.87,0:03:44.06,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Promise me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.56,0:03:46.56,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to school tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.95,0:03:50.45,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so happy! I love you, Kirin!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.01,0:03:54.61,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.61,0:03:56.76,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,There's someone else you love...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.41,0:04:00.31,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,The person I love the most is myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.80,0:04:02.64,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,In the end, I'm just a narcissist.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.19,0:04:06.05,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm obedient to Lady Shinobu because of my love to myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.00,0:04:13.85,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I guess... me loving you is... bothersome to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.06,0:04:15.00,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,You know...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.52,0:04:18.44,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not the woman you imagine me to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.97,0:04:22.58,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Since Lady Shinobu is around, I can somehow cope.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.08,0:04:25.16,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,In fact, I'm just a good-for-nothing...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.16,0:04:26.36,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't say that!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.74,0:04:27.63,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.96,0:04:31.28,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought of myself as a weak girl, one unwilling to get out of bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.87,0:04:35.59,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Enjoying a bag of potato chips by my pillow.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.78,0:04:38.45,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Regardless, you're still you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.45,0:04:41.14,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,You're still my sweet Kirin.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.22,0:04:44.12,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, stop that!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.53,0:04:48.42,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Matsuri!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.74,0:04:50.15,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Please touch me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.28,0:04:56.29,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,You do this with Lady Shinobu, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.29,0:04:58.84,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Do it with me too, just for tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.25,0:05:03.89,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Keep it a secret from Lady Shinobu.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.01,0:05:07.56,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Kirin!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.56,0:05:09.05,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Keep it down!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.56,0:06:37.63,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Seems to me that everybody's lively and healthy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.85,0:06:39.40,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Sarcastic, aren't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.58,0:06:41.55,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,What else can we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.55,0:06:44.28,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,We could come down with mumps anytime now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.01,0:06:47.25,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,It'd be a disaster if the virus spreads, don't you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.82,0:06:50.12,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,And... what of the sick person?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.62,0:06:52.37,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,She's under quarantine in the next room.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.63,0:06:54.64,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you call a doctor to check on her?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.84,0:06:56.37,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Most certainly!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.37,0:06:58.69,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Kirin's on the job!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.17,0:07:02.17,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,She's the only one with experience in this matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.95,0:07:04.94,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Here you go!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.52,0:07:06.37,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.95,0:07:08.97,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,So, what's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.21,0:07:10.19,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Did something happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.45,0:07:12.96,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,That's my line!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.96,0:07:17.64,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks to the absence of you girls, Miss Hayato sent me here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.12,0:07:20.20,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,To hand you these printouts!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.35,0:07:21.60,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.35,0:07:24.47,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Show me your notes while you're at it, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.68,0:07:26.23,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright then.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.42,0:07:28.74,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,And join us for dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.91,0:07:30.48,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,But the rules...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.67,0:07:33.08,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Momoko, it's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.08,0:07:34.75,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Have dinner with us!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.94,0:07:36.12,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Chizuru...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.83,0:07:38.75,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Now that I think about it, the fridge's empty.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.02,0:07:40.55,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Order something, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.55,0:07:41.65,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Something scrumptious.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.82,0:07:43.15,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Good idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.37,0:07:45.64,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Lady Shinobu, I want pizza!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.89,0:07:48.54,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,I think sushi's better...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.54,0:07:49.69,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,What about you, Lady Shinobu?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.85,0:07:52.53,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to have the same as Lady Shinobu!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.74,0:07:54.87,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,What would you like, Lady Shinobu?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.07,0:07:56.54,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.32,0:07:59.54,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,"Lady" Shinobu...?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.76,0:08:03.47,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Lady Shinobu, I'd like what Ai had for her snack.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.71,0:08:05.24,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.93,0:08:22.83,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Matsuri... Could this be your first time?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.74,0:08:25.83,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.18,0:08:26.92,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.37,0:08:29.55,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Then what were you using this for?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.55,0:08:31.05,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You got it wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.20,0:08:32.84,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,That's my friend's...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.65,0:08:35.28,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.84,0:08:38.16,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Kirin... it's embarrassing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.40,0:08:44.20,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Just for tonight, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.58,0:08:47.40,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Kirin!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.71,0:08:48.39,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Ki-
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.38,0:08:51.76,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't push it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.99,0:08:53.62,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me you love me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.29,0:08:58.99,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,I love you! I really love you! Kirin, I love you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.79,0:09:07.50,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,My, you're really wet.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.27,0:09:10.09,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Matsuri, does it feel good?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.82,0:09:11.53,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.56,0:09:16.10,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going... I'm going to come!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.45,0:09:29.24,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry. It'll take a while longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.67,0:09:31.80,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for the red umbrella.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.28,0:09:36.30,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Our dorm feels different compared to yours, doesn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.65,0:09:39.28,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Well... our place is normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.87,0:09:41.98,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,It's special here, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.66,0:09:44.33,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Special children, special circumstances.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.84,0:09:47.20,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Family issues, so to speak.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.02,0:09:50.58,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why this is home to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.43,0:09:53.79,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone in the class is... family.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.71,0:09:58.71,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Those girls like you a lot, don't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.46,0:10:00.38,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,I know, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.62,0:10:03.01,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,They're so adorable!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.24,0:10:05.10,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Kissing and hugging...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.60,0:10:08.23,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,What about you, Miss Naito?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.64,0:10:10.61,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Ever kissed and hugged someone?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.14,0:10:13.80,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't had my first kiss yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.14,0:10:16.22,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't say...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.95,0:10:24.69,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Not yet, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.77,0:10:29.95,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Unlike me, the dashing Handa sure is thriving, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.63,0:10:32.89,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Love's everywhere, like there's a mega sale.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.54,0:10:34.83,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.08,0:10:36.41,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.16,0:10:41.97,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm grateful to them for showering me with their love.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.79,0:10:47.43,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,But, I still haven't told anyone that I love them.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.62,0:10:50.85,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.11,0:10:53.14,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.89,0:10:58.19,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Momoko Naito.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.49,0:11:00.24,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.34,0:11:05.33,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.75,0:11:08.67,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,...better get going.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.71,0:11:19.74,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,See you later!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.10,0:11:39.59,Signs,,0000,0030,0320,,{\fad(0,0)\pos(500,141)}{\p1}{\bord1.5\shad0}m 0 0 l 270 0 270 130 0 130{\p0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.10,0:11:39.59,Signs - Text,,0000,0030,0320,,{\fad(0,0)\an7\fs28\pos(372,29)}Harmonica Performance
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.10,0:11:39.59,Signs - Text,,0000,0030,0320,,{\fad(0,0)\an7\fs28\pos(372,29)}_________________________
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.10,0:11:39.59,Signs - Text,,0000,0030,0320,,{\fad(0,0)\an7\fs28\pos(372,59)}Twinkle Twinkle Little Star 5+3
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.10,0:11:39.59,Signs - Text,,0000,0030,0320,,{\fad(0,0)\an7\fs28\pos(372,89)}When the Saints go Marching in
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.29,0:12:13.93,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Ma'am, I'm done.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.34,0:12:15.29,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Good job.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.08,0:12:18.09,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,From tomorrow onwards, I'm free after school.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.01,0:12:20.86,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,But only until the cultural festival is over.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.46,0:12:22.94,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,That's great!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.94,0:12:25.97,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,It'd be troublesome if no one went home.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.25,0:12:27.14,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Wouldn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.51,0:12:28.98,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have any spare time later?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.28,0:12:32.36,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have plans?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.04,0:12:34.48,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Again?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.84,0:12:37.79,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,We're ready to perform "When the Saints Go Marching In" at the cultural festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.79,0:12:42.26,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,I promised everybody a printout of the Japanese translation of the lyrics.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.82,0:12:44.73,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,But my English has gotten rusty.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.37,0:12:47.12,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a math teacher!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.12,0:12:48.69,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, here we go again.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.50,0:12:50.02,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Please?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.34,0:12:51.96,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you ask me...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.65,0:12:55.33,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Please! Help me with the translation!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.03,0:12:57.81,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Your English is great, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.11,0:12:59.17,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Honestly...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.36,0:13:01.13,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess there's really no other way...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.13,0:13:04.58,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,As expected! The Naito Shrine works!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.35,0:13:06.78,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Shrine?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.45,0:13:18.43,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess it's gotten late, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.77,0:13:20.68,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you hungry?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.23,0:13:22.80,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm starving to death!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.38,0:13:25.46,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go eat something good!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.28,0:13:27.58,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,I want ramen!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.77,0:13:29.10,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.87,0:13:56.40,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,You know, I had no idea that "When the Saints Go Marching In" was a requiem.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.64,0:14:00.36,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Moreover, I didn't know that it was an American folk song.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.90,0:14:02.54,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Were you aware of that, Miss Naito?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.02,0:14:03.91,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.40,0:14:05.51,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Guess not, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.87,0:14:08.25,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Great, there's someone like me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.28,0:14:11.39,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.79,0:14:13.92,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Why go to a hotel just for ramen?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.54,0:14:16.68,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder why...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.29,0:14:19.19,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,I just thought you'd like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.81,0:14:22.19,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you a gourmet eater, Miss Naito?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.84,0:14:24.98,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I just love to eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.72,0:14:29.55,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,And lately, it seems like something is been bothering you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.67,0:14:31.29,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,You're pretty observant.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.60,0:14:32.66,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,You know me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.95,0:14:36.89,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,You're very mature.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.29,0:14:39.73,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just a naïve kid to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.18,0:14:46.49,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.91,0:14:48.44,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it alright to have seconds?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.72,0:14:49.77,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Go ahead!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.65,0:14:58.30,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.86,0:15:01.65,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,You've eaten here before, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.04,0:15:03.50,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Was it on a date?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.06,0:15:05.64,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you spend the night here?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.09,0:15:06.98,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,I suppose I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.26,0:15:08.77,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,That's so nice!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.12,0:15:12.85,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, now. Don't you go around saying that to boys.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.37,0:15:15.78,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,It'd be basically the same as inviting them.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.10,0:15:17.35,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.81,0:15:18.67,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, it would.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.04,0:15:22.34,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,If I were a guy, I'd definitely go with the flow.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.75,0:15:25.62,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,No. Even if I were, it'd still be bad for a teacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.61,0:15:30.87,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,If you were me, I'd invite you to a place with a nice night view.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.65,0:15:33.20,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,No thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.87,0:15:36.65,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Why not? That's boring.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.88,0:15:37.91,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,At first...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.39,0:15:40.82,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't want to think of you as the flirtatious type.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.35,0:15:43.84,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the second invitation.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.68,0:16:22.30,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,I've...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.30,0:16:24.81,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,...always been seen as naïve.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.07,0:16:26.23,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Being naïve is fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.54,0:16:29.44,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know how to act like I'm not.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.24,0:16:31.86,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll teach you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.10,0:16:35.28,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sick of being a good girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.56,0:16:40.71,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Sometimes, I want to get off the railing and fly freely.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.33,0:16:44.22,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,When that happens, feel free to call me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.48,0:17:11.39,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you ever done this with another woman before?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.86,0:17:12.80,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.42,0:17:14.58,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you jealous?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.83,0:17:16.16,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to know.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.95,0:17:31.93,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Momoko, could this be your first?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.02,0:17:33.77,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.59,0:17:37.69,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,From now on, I will teach you a lot of fun things.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.09,0:17:45.69,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,My first time was around your age, Momoko.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.79,0:17:51.73,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Whilst pretty, she was a gloomy girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.92,0:17:56.17,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,I had the chance of getting chocolate from her on Valentine's Day.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.46,0:17:58.90,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,But in the end...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.22,0:18:00.95,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,She passed away.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.66,0:18:04.71,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.71,0:18:08.91,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Her sexual ability \Nwas commendable.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.95,0:18:11.77,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Ma'am...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.49,0:18:13.28,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.21,0:18:35.33,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,You're kidding!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.33,0:18:36.67,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.88,0:18:38.92,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,A girl from the neighboring class saw them!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.17,0:18:42.20,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Weren't they just at the hotel's lounge or lobby?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.20,0:18:43.63,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Nope, that's not it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.82,0:18:46.02,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,She saw them coming out from a room!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.91,0:18:49.16,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Gosh! That settles it, then!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.19,0:18:51.45,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,They seemed to get along, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.45,0:18:55.36,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Unbelievable! Who would have thought that Miss Hayato and Naito were...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.54,0:18:56.86,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.13,0:19:12.01,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, have you heard?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.04,0:19:13.68,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,The rumour about Miss Hayato.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.09,0:19:15.66,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,I was surprised!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.10,0:19:16.93,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Her lover was...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.93,0:19:17.57,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Maya!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.90,0:19:19.31,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.00,0:19:24.19,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Lady Shinobu?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.47,0:19:25.94,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't you notice?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.29,0:19:27.82,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,You even live with her...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.29,0:19:32.97,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,You know that Lady Shinobu has feelings for someone, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.32,0:19:34.03,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.24,0:19:36.35,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Miss Naito!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.96,0:19:50.45,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys! Miss Hayato collapsed!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.83,0:20:12.71,Signs,,0000,0030,0320,,{\fad(800,800)}{\pos(320,75)}{\p1}{\bord0.5\shad0}m 0 0 l 600 0 600 50 0 50{\p0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.83,0:20:12.71,Signs - Text,,0000,0030,0320,,{\fad(800,800)\fs30\pos(320,70)}Welcome to the annual Kagome Girls High School Cultural Festival
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.38,0:20:02.85,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,This way, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.32,0:20:16.81,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Romeo! Wherefore art thou Romeo?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.84,0:20:21.32,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Go! Go! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.82,0:20:30.32,Signs,,0000,0030,0320,,{\fad(0,0)}{\pos(320,125)}{\p1}{\bord0.5\shad0}m 0 0 l 400 0 400 100 0 100{\p0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.82,0:20:30.32,Signs - Text,,0000,0030,0320,,{\fad(0,0)\fs30\pos(320,115)}NOTICE: The Harmonica act has been canceled.\N- Kagome Girls High School
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.94,0:20:39.86,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Momoko!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.34,0:20:42.22,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.68,0:20:43.57,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Go on ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.54,0:20:46.59,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Chizuru! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.00,0:20:49.05,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry! I'm really sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.82,0:21:02.32,Signs,,0000,0030,0320,,{\fad(0,0)}{\pos(320,75)}{\p1}{\bord0.5\shad0}m 0 0 l 260 0 260 50 0 50{\p0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.82,0:21:02.32,Signs - Text,,0000,0030,0320,,{\fs30\pos(320,70)}Mathematics Preparation Room
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.32,0:21:17.36,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Hayato...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.78,0:21:22.24,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Is anyone in there?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.72,0:21:25.52,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,No one's in there?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.31,0:21:28.35,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,No one, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.46,0:21:30.08,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,We're coming in!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.93,0:21:34.98,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, I think this is a bad idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.64,0:21:38.23,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,If it's here, then no one will come.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.45,0:21:41.43,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Since Miss Hayato is in the hospital now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.54,0:21:44.05,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Or rather, she resigned from school.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.65,0:21:47.37,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,She has some serious illness.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.64,0:21:49.80,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,She was a nice teacher, wasn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.04,0:21:52.70,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if this room will be cleared out.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.24,0:21:56.33,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no harm in using it until then.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.98,0:21:57.75,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.01,0:22:00.54,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't speak. Do it seriously.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.93,0:22:01.92,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,So she says.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.32,0:22:03.18,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.68,0:22:06.05,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though you'll come pretty quickly!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.39,0:22:10.47,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-That feels great!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.64,0:22:12.60,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Nori!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.71,0:22:20.43,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you come already?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.11,0:22:21.58,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.27,0:22:23.14,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,I just came!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.43,0:22:25.55,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Please! I'm gonna come again!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.99,0:22:27.97,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.39,0:22:38.83,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,That was suffocating!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.57,0:22:42.62,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,What were you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.12,0:22:47.03,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,While trying to run away from some senior that was hard to deal with, I ended up hiding here.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.70,0:22:49.62,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't like associating myself with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.96,0:22:50.97,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.70,0:22:52.86,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,What about you, Miss Naito?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.69,0:22:55.64,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Asking you might be a bad idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.94,0:22:59.14,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,I... In order to avoid other people...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.27,0:23:03.28,Signs,,0000,0030,0320,,{\fad(800,800)}{\pos(320,105)}{\p1}{\bord0.5\shad0}m 0 0 l 450 0 450 80 0 80{\p0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.27,0:23:03.28,Signs - Text,,0000,0030,0320,,{\fad(800,800)\fs30\pos(320,100)}Sorry... I will be transferring to a faraway hospital.\NPlease forget about me. - Hayato Kyouko
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.83,0:23:07.14,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you... not seen her since then?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.77,0:23:09.76,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,No visitors were allowed...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.76,0:23:11.34,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,It should be fine now, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.68,0:23:14.42,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,The teachers went to ask about her.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.05,0:23:17.72,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,It'd be an annoyance to her if I went.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.68,0:23:21.27,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,But you want to see her, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.10,0:23:24.29,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Then just go and see her!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.62,0:23:27.18,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not that simple!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.64,0:23:29.50,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Stubborn as ever...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.74,0:23:33.70,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Sometimes, you should get off the railing and fly freely.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.30,0:23:38.15,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.48,0:23:42.48,Main Font,,0000,0000,0130,,{\fs70\fad(0,0)\fnFlorence\b1\pos(334,204)}At a quick pace...{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.98,0:23:45.99,Main Font,,0000,0000,0130,,{\fs70\fad(0,0)\fnFlorence\b1\pos(326,373)}Faster...{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.32,0:23:51.29,Main Font,,0000,0000,0120,,{\fs70\fad(0,0)\fnFlorence\b1\pos(326,373)}As fast as I can...{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.34,0:23:48.32,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait up!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.31,0:24:13.31,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Momoko...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.63,0:24:20.04,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Running away without even a goodbye...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.04,0:24:21.13,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not fair.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.86,0:24:24.61,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me you want to break up properly!
